item.title: CVE-2023-31405|2024-08-02T14:53:30.779Z -- sap_se -- sap%20netweaver%20as%20for%20java%20%28log%20viewer%29
item.description: SAP NetWeaver AS for Java - versions ENGINEAPI 7.50, SERVERCORE 7.50, J2EE-APPS 7.50, allows an unauthenticated attacker to craft a request over the network which can result in unwarranted modifications to a system log without user interaction. There is no ability to view any information or any effect on availability.
